    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant restoration or may serve best as a parts car. The engine currently does not turn over, and there are visible signs of heavy rust along the frame and lower body panels. Inside, the upholstery is heavily torn, and several dashboard components are non-functional. The exterior paint is severely faded with multiple dents and deep scratches throughout. This is a true project vehicle for someone with the mechanical expertise to perform a complete overhaul.",
